{"word":"Pentecost","slug":"pentecost","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pentecost</b> Called:<br/> - Feast of Weeks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=22'>Exo 34:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=10'>Deu 16:10</a> <br/> - Feast of Harvest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=16'>Exo 23:16</a> <br/> - Day of First Fruits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=26'>Num 28:26</a> <br/> - Day of Pentecost<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=1'>Act 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=16'>Act 20:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=16&verse=8'>1Co 16:8</a> <br/> Institution of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=16'>Exo 23:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=22'>Exo 34:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=21'>Lev 23:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=31'>Num 28:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=12'>Deu 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=16'>Deu 16:16</a><br/> Holy Ghost given to the apostles on the first day of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2'>Act 2</a><br/><a href='S:Feasts'>Feasts</a>"}]}